import React from 'react'
import { Nav, NavbarContainer, NavLogo, MobileIcons, NavMenu, NavItem, NavLinks} from './NavbarElements'

const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Nav>
                <NavbarContainer>
                    <NavLogo to="/"> dolla </NavLogo>
                    <MobileIcon>
                        <FaBars />

                    <NavMenu>
                        <NavItem>
                            <NavLinks to="about">About</NavLinks>
                        </NavItem>
                    </NavMenu>
                </NavbarContainer>
            </Nav>
        </>
    );
};

export default Navbar
